---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Mathilde Godard — French photographer and video post-producer based in Nantes, France. Portrait, fashion, travel, architecture and landscape."
>
  <div class="about">

    <!-- ── Page header ── -->
    <header class="about__header container">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1 class="about__title display">Hi there,</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- ── Main content ── -->
    <div class="about__content container">

      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="about__text">
        <p>
          Here is a little portrait of myself from the past few years.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am a French artist from Brittany who has sought out adventures and travel to enrich
          both my art and understanding of the world. I cherish nature and have a curious mind.
          I see life and our surroundings as a playground to be explored and I wish to highlight
          its beauty. My art is the reflection of this outlook and I hope to spark other people's
          curiosity through my work.
        </p>
        <p>
          I photograph my day to day life with my Olympus om-10, an old film camera. I like to
          wander across the streets and stop at random coffee places searching for people's smiles
          while drinking my tea. I've lived in London for 4 and a half years where I have come
          across amazing people and made friends. There, I became a post producer working in
          agencies and production houses. I loved my job and particularly the people that I was
          working with. My colleagues were amazing, inspiring and creative. Next to my main job
          I've taken up opportunities to direct music videos and photographed fashion campaigns,
          artists and musicians.
        </p>

 

        <p>
          Living in London city never put me off traveling. I went to Iceland, Germany, Spain,
          and to Canada where I ended up falling in love. Life is full of surprises and so I've
          decided to leave London to go to the other side of the world. Because like my partner
          I am one of those who seek adventures. This time I took off to New Zealand. I wanted
          to live surrounded by nature with my partner in a van we built and named Waka as a
          reference for Maori canoe. We crossed the entire country during 2&frac12; years aboard
          in our van going from one adventure to another. We shared incredible moments and met so
          many bright souls throughout our journey, nature was luxurious and roads were endless.
          We've learned things that we would never have the opportunity to learn before and I feel
          immensely grateful for all those experiences.
        </p>

        <!-- Inline photo 2 -->
        <figure class="about__figure about__figure--portrait">
          <img
            src="/images/about/mathilde-camera.webp"
            alt="Mathilde Godard taking a photo"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>

        <p>
          I am now based in France where I ask myself what will be my next creative project or
          my next encounters. I enjoy collaborative projects and am always happy to take pictures
          or direct videos.
        </p>
        <p>
          Don't hesitate to reach me if you are looking for a photographer, a post-producer or
          a videographer. I look forward to working with you in the future.
        </p>

        <!-- Sign-off -->
        <p class="about__signoff display">With love,<br />Mathilde</p>

        <!-- Socials -->
        <div class="about__socials">
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/mathildegodard__/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="about__social-link"
            aria-label="Instagram"
          >
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/>
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="0.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
            </svg>
            <span>@mathildegodard__</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mathilde-godard-2915998b/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="about__social-link"
            aria-label="LinkedIn"
          >
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/>
              <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/>
              <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Mathilde Godard</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:contact@mathildegodard.com"
            class="about__social-link"
            aria-label="Email"
          >
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/>
              <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span>contact@mathildegodard.com</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="about__sidebar">
        <div class="about__sidebar-photo">
          <img
            src="/images/about/mathilde-nature.webp"
            alt="Mathilde Godard"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="about__sidebar-info">
          <div class="about__info-block">
            <span class="eyebrow">Based in</span>
            <p>Nantes, France</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about__info-block">
            <span class="eyebrow">Available for</span>
            <ul>
              <li>Photography</li>
              <li>Video direction</li>
              <li>Post-production</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="about__info-block">
            <span class="eyebrow">Specialities</span>
            <ul>
              <li>Portrait</li>
              <li>Fashion & editorial</li>
              <li>Travel & documentary</li>
              <li>Architecture</li>
              <li>Landscape</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style lang="scss">
@use '../styles/variables' as *;
@use '../styles/mixins' as *;

.about {
  padding-top: calc(#{$nav-height} + 5rem);
  padding-bottom: 8rem;

  // ── Header ──
  &__header {
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid $border;
  }

  &__title {
    font-size: clamp(52px, 10vw, 120px);
    color: $white;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  // ── Two-column layout ──
  &__content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding-top: 5rem;

    @include desktop {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    @include tablet {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  // ── Text column ──
  &__text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 680px;

    p {
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba($text, 0.8);

      &:first-child {
        font-family: $font-display;
        font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px);
        font-weight: 300;
        color: $white;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
    }
  }

  // ── Inline figures ──
  &__figure {
    margin: 1rem 0;

    img {
      width: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    figcaption {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: $muted;
    }

    &--wide img {
      max-height: 520px;
      object-position: center top;
    }

    &--portrait {
      max-width: 460px;

      img {
        aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      }
    }
  }

  // ── Sign-off ──
  &__signoff {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px) !important;
    color: $white !important;
    line-height: 1.3 !important;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid $border;
  }

  // ── Socials ──
  &__socials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  &__social-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: $muted;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: color 0.2s;

    svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

    &:hover { color: $accent; }
  }

  // ── Sidebar ──
  &__sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(#{$nav-height} + 2rem);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;

    @include tablet {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    @include mobile {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  &__sidebar-photo {
    overflow: hidden;

    img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      transition: transform 0.6s $ease-out-expo;

      &:hover { transform: scale(1.03); }
    }
  }

  &__sidebar-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  &__info-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;

    p, ul { color: rgba($text, 0.7); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.3rem;

      li {
        padding-left: 1rem;
        position: relative;

        &::before {
          content: '—';
          position: absolute;
          left: 0;
          color: $border;
          font-size: 12px;
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</style>
